  "texts": [
    "Methods compared in trimodal mosaic integration tasks.Multigrate.",
    "The Python package Multigrate 29 (v0.0.2) is available at https://github.com/theislab/multigrate.",
    "For data inputs, we took the intersection of genes in scRNA-seq data and proteins in ADT data across different batches.",
    "We processed the data using the default method of Multigrate.",
    "The values of parameters KL and integ were set to 0.1 and 3,000, respectively.Fig. 1 |1Fig."
  ]
}